sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DataPlane as DataPlane<br/>(V2 Protocol Handler)
    participant Batcher as AdaptiveBatcher
    participant Runtime as Inference Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lightgbm/onnx)
    participant Models as Model Storage<br/>/mnt/models
    participant Metrics as MetricsServer<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant OTEL as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over Client,Gateway: Flow 1: REST Model Inference
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443 | Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS
    RBAC->>REST: After RBAC check<br/>HTTP/8080 | plaintext (pod-local)
    REST->>DataPlane: Inference request
    DataPlane->>Batcher: Queue for batching
    Batcher->>Runtime: Batched inference
    Runtime->>Models: Load model artifacts<br/>File I/O
    Models-->>Runtime: Model data
    Runtime-->>Batcher: Prediction result
    Batcher-->>DataPlane: Batched response
    DataPlane-->>REST: V2 InferenceResponse
    REST-->>RBAC: JSON Response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,gRPC: Flow 2: gRPC Model Inference
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>gRPC: Forward<br/>gRPC/HTTP2/8081 | plaintext (pod-local)
    gRPC->>DataPlane: Inference request
    DataPlane->>Runtime: Model inference
    Runtime-->>DataPlane: Prediction result
    DataPlane-->>gRPC: InferenceResponse
    gRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC/HTTPS Response

    Note over Kafka,Runtime: Flow 3: Kafka Event-Driven (Optional)
    Kafka->>DataPlane: Consume inference event<br/>Kafka/9092 | Configurable
    DataPlane->>Runtime: Model inference
    Runtime-->>DataPlane: Prediction result
    DataPlane->>Kafka: Produce result event<br/>Kafka/9092 | Configurable

    Note over Prom,Metrics: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082 | plaintext
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics

    Note over DataPlane,OTEL: Flow 5: Distributed Tracing
    DataPlane->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | plaintext | OTLP
